high_descs: Turn around and walk to the diningtable.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Head out the room and turn right to walk down the passage and turn left to reach the apple at the end of the passage.
Cut the red apple into slices with the knife.
Cut the green apple into slices with the knife and close the box.
Turn around to walk out the passage and turn left to reach the drawer.
Put the knife in the top left drawer of the dresser.
Head to the apple on the left to reach the box.
Open the box and pick up the green slice of apple.
Turn around to the end of the passage and turn right to walk down the passage and turn left to reach the microwave.
Put the slice of green apple in the microwave.
Turn around and head out the room and turn right to walk down the passage and turn left to reach the apple box at the end of the passage.
Open the box and pick up the red slice of apple.
Turn around to the end of the passage and turn right to walk down the passage and turn left to reach the microwave.
Put the slice of red apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the slice of red and green Apple in the Microwave.

high_descs: Walk around the circular diningtable next to you until you reach the knife.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Walk around the apple to the left, entering the hall with two paths, then take the path on the right, then take a left to the box on the floor.
Slice up the red apple in the box on the right.
Slice up the green apple in the box.
Turn around, go straight and take a left into the bedroom, approaching the drawers to the immediate left.
Place the knife inside the drawer.
Return to the box with the cut up apples.
Pick up a slice of the green apple.
Return to the room with the circular table, heading towards the microwave at the end of the room.
Place the apple slice into the microwave.
Return to the box with the cut up apples.
Pick up a slice of the red apple.
Return to the microwave.
Place the apple slice into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a single green Apple slice with a single red Apple slice in a Microwave.
